ACADEMIC ATTRIBUTION

This software implements the BeCoMe method and was developed at Czech University
of Life Sciences Prague, Faculty of Economics and Management.

Author: Ekaterina Kuzmina
Year: 2025/2026

ORIGINAL METHOD AND CITATION

This implementation is based on the BeCoMe method. If you use this software in
academic work, please cite the original paper:

Vrana, I., Tyrychtr, J., & Pelikán, M. (2021). BeCoMe: Easy-to-implement
optimized method for best-compromise group decision making: Flood-prevention
and COVID-19 case studies. Environmental Modelling & Software, 136, 104953.
https://doi.org/10.1016/j.envsoft.2020.104953
